title: Carly Simon Live From Martha's Vinyard (1987)
description:
Carly Simon Live From Martha's Vinyard 1987.

Selected singles:

1. You're So Vain
2. Nobody Does It Better
3. You Belong To Me

That had the effect of having my account automatically deleted.
